Class AVLTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • AVLTree

  • public class AVLTree
extends java.lang.Object
    The AVLTree class implements a self-balancing AVL binary search tree where insertion, deletion, and lookup are guaranteed to take O(log n) in the worst- case. The tree is maintained by ensuring that the heights of each node's child subtrees differ by at most 1.
    Since:
    2018-10-03
